{"tid":1704793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】玻利維亞政局變天！","createTime":"2019-11-10T21:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T11:31:31.000Z","uid":296674,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c016ca6e67dea85787ef511fdae45b27bc7748","tid":1704793,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T21:26:33.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞總統莫拉雷斯宣布辭職，佢本來係拉丁美洲在任最耐嘅領導人。<br />\n佢史無前例地利用最高法院推翻公投結果，修改憲法令到自己可以第四次參選，然後被指利用種票令自己可以連任，引起大規模反政府示威，示威者焚燒選舉事務處建築物，甚至連當地警察亦叛變加入反政府示威行列。其中一位女警察接受電視訪問時流淚向民眾宣告，警察嘅職責必然係保護人民，企係民眾嘅一邊。<br />\n<br />\n－－－<br />\n呢個故事嘅寓意係，極權總有倒台嘅一日<br />\n黎明前總係最黑暗嘅<br />\n黑警唔想做condom，最好快快篤灰<br />\n香港人反抗"},{"pid":"4d861128b83598e2a9f98034535869a42a99f733","tid":1704793,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T21:30:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cbsnews.com/news/bolivia-elections-president-evo-morales-resigns-today-after-reelection-fraud-protests-live-updates-2019-11-10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fbolivia-elections-president-evo-morales-resigns-today-after-reelection-fraud-protests-live-updates-2019-11-10%2F&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=7d941a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbsnews.com/news/bolivia-elections-president-evo-morales-resigns-today-after-reelection-fraud-protests-live-updates-2019-11-10/</a>"},{"pid":"470425c7d3d5dc70b1656b4794a97c52ca763afc","tid":1704793,"uid":3212,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T21:31:49.000Z","msg":"重點係人地軍方係傾向人民，班甴曱只會奶共産黨袋底"},{"pid":"55284d62c3caf04b570870b42b955f714858ed85","tid":1704793,"uid":305954,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T21:33:01.000Z","msg":"班警甴智商唔過80點會識咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35420d4fb2bdcb21f0108d37a9c2576d94cc0157","tid":1704793,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470425c7d3d5dc70b1656b4794a97c